{"service_name": "Rivo Corporate Risk Management Platform Services", "service_id": "4763050397663232", "company_name": "Extended Content Solutions Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Extended Content Solutions Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Rivo Corporate Risk Management Platform Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    The Extended Content Solutions (ECS) specialist cloud services offering for Rivo provides expertise and support for deploying, configuring and integrating Rivo\u2019s market leading cloud software platform. The Rivo SaaS platform provides corporate risk management solutions for Health, Safety, Environmental, Quality, Governance, Compliance Wellbeing &amp; Sustainability.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Cloud SaaS platform - browser accessed, no install\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Flexible form-based online apps for data capture\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Mobile enabled including offline capability\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Powerful advanced data visualisation tool for dashboard reporting\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Highly configurable and flexible implementation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Tier-5 disaster recovery (ISO 27001 certified)\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     SaaS solution offers rapid set up and implemnetation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Simplifies the management of corporate obligation compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf Health and Safety recording system\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf audit management solution\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf training and competency management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf legal compliance management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf Wellbeing management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf asset management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf risk assessment management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Off the shelf document management system\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3850 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92693/4763050397663232-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92693/4763050397663232-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92693/4763050397663232-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n  